
sequenceDiagram
    participant Driver
    participant Pedal
    participant Injector
    participant ExplosionChamber
    participant Crankshaft
    participant Transmission
    participant Wheel

    Note over Driver,Wheel: Acceleration Flow (Association Chain)
    Driver->>Pedal: use(p_pression)
    Pedal->>Injector: execute(p_pression)
    Injector->>ExplosionChamber: explode()
    ExplosionChamber->>Crankshaft: receiveForce()
    Crankshaft->>Transmission: activate(p_force)
    Transmission->>Wheel: rotate()
    Wheel-->>Driver: Car accelerates